#leave_policy.txt
Employees are entitled to 18 days of paid annual leave per calendar year. Leave must be requested at least 3 days in advance and approved by the reporting manager. Unused annual leave up to 10 days can be carried forward to the next year.
#code_of_conduct.md
# Code of Conduct

## Scope
This code applies to all employees, interns, and contractors.

## Professional Behavior
- Treat colleagues, clients, and partners with respect.
- Harassment or discrimination of any kind is not tolerated.

## Use of Company Assets
- Use company devices and accounts primarily for business purposes.
- Do not share passwords or confidential information with unauthorized persons.

## Confidentiality
- Protect customer and company data.
- Follow all information security and privacy policies.

## Reporting Violations
- Report suspected violations to HR or your manager.
- Violations may result in disciplinary action, up to and including termination.
